name: NEW! Muck Fe - album
description:
This is the long awaited, self released album from the band. It  includes a couple of the tracks on the Our Nation EP and also a number of new tracks ...... 

1. Officer
2. Read All ABout It
3. Our Nation (on the EP)
4. The Folk Song
5. Man About A Dog
6. Social Suicide (on the EP)
7. Youe Mean Nothing To Me
8. These Drugs (Don't Love You)
9. Better Than Me (interlude)
10. Better than Me
11. The 7th of the Cow's Milk

You can also download the album via a number of retailers by going to the band's MySpace page and checking out the player where there are links to the various retailers.

The best £5 you ever spent! Enjoy!

(Price includes postage to the UK aswell!)
